    public class StandardInsuranceCompany
extends InsuranceCompany
implements java.io.Serializable

    class StandardInsuranceCompany

    Instance of this class represents a normal non-state fully functional insurance_pac company It has customer register, offer catalog, billing information and other fields and Arraylists It also enables customers to be added and deleted from registers implements CompanyBasic, CompanyBasic.CompanyDeletions, Serializable
    Since:
    2019
    Author:
    Maros Kusnir
